            "title": "日股初段靠穩　曾升穿4萬點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東京股市初段上升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經指數一度升穿4萬點，但未能企穩，較早時報39959點，升57點，升幅0.15%。</p>\n</div>",
